<h4>
    White and Black Items
</h4>


<ul class = 'principleList'>
    <li>
        An object that is white <strong>reflects every color</strong>.
    </li>
    <li>
        An object that is block <strong>absorbs every color</strong>.
    </li>
    <li>
        White light is made from all colors of light put together, so when
        every color is reflected, something appears white.
    </li>
    <li>
        Black is the absence of light, so when all colors are absorbed, something appaers
        black.
    </li>
</ul>

